BRUEGHEL. 2 types of foliage: 1) Broad-oak leaves; 2) Rarer: pointillist in small brushstrokes not points: (also in Washington, see also 'Landscape with Huntsman' Koetser 1970 & 1972 spring exhibition and freer version Wulc); Landscape: Sale Sotheby, 21-3-73 (78), River on Outskirts of a Town; The Washington Picture by the same hand as the Koetser Version of the Huntsmen in a Forest?
